snippet.title: GENIE Reprise - Trailer (eastasiasoft)
snippet.description: Take the role of Lula and explore a vibrant fantasy world as she journeys to discover the meaning of the Genie and fulfill her destiny! GENIE Reprise is an atmospheric fantasy adventure told through fully voiced poetry and 3D first-person exploration.
